Tadka
Oil and add cumin, add okra/carrot (once nicely fried, put beans), once everything fried, then add (1 spoon chili powder, 1-1/2 spoon of
coriander powder, 1/5-2/5 of haldi, salt accordingly and kitchen king at the end as well. If needed, can add tomato puree (very little).
Also optional add one or two spoons of yogurt. 
